<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ESS 최신 정보 - ESS-M.S</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/1.main.css">
    <style>
        /* 페이지 전용 추가 스타일 */
        .sub-hero {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .board { padding: 50px 0; min-height: 500px; }
        .board-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
        .board-table th { border-top: 2px solid #333; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .board-table td { border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; }
        .pagination a { display: inline-block; padding: 8px 16px; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #333; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; }
        .pagination a.active { background-color: #007bff; color: white; border-color: #007bff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="logo" onclick="location.href='1.main.html'" style="cursor:pointer;">ESS-M.S</h1>
            <nav>
                <ul id="nav-list">
                    <li><a href="1.main.html">홈</a></li>
                    <li><a href="3.serviceInfo.html">서비스 소개</a></li>
                    <li><a href="2.contact.html">문의게시판</a></li>
                    <li id="auth-menu">
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="login-btn" onclick="openLoginWindow()">로그인</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="sub-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>ESS 최신 정보</h2>
            <p>에너지 저장 장치(ESS) 시장의 최신 트렌드와 기술 정보를 전해드립니다.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main class="container board">
        <div class="board-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <p>총 <strong>4</strong>개의 소식이 있습니다.</p>
            <div class="search-box">
                <input type="text" placeholder="검색어 입력" style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;">
                <button class="btn" style="padding: 8px 15px; margin-left: 5px; background:#007bff; color:white; border:none; border-radius:4px; cursor:pointer;">검색</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <table class="board-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 80px; text-align: center;">번호</th>
                    <th>제목</th>
                    <th style="width: 120px;">작성일</th>
                    <th style="width: 80px; text-align: center;">조회</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">4</td>
                    <td>
                        <a href="8.news_view.html?id=4" style="text-decoration: none; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">[기술] 차세대 배터리 매니지먼트 시스템(BMS) 효율 측정 결과</a>
                    </td>
                    <td>2024-03-20</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">125</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">3</td>
                    <td>
                        <a href="8.news_view.html?id=3" style="text-decoration: none; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">[공지] ESS-M.S 모니터링 시스템 정기 점검 안내 (3/25)</a>
                    </td>
                    <td>2024-03-18</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">48</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">2</td>
                    <td>
                        <a href="8.news_view.html?id=2" style="text-decoration: none; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">[업계] 2024년 상반기 에너지 정책 변화와 ESS 시장 전망</a>
                    </td>
                    <td>2024-03-15</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">210</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">1</td>
                    <td>
                        <a href="8.news_view.html?id=1" style="text-decoration: none; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">[보도] 당사 모니터링 시스템, 에너지 효율 대상 수상</a>
                    </td>
                    <td>2024-03-10</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">89</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="pagination" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
            <a href="#" class="active">1</a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer style="background-color: #2c3e50; color: white; padding: 40px 0;">
        <div class="container footer-content" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <div class="footer-info">
                <h2 class="footer-logo" style="margin-bottom:10px;">ESS-M.S</h2>
                <p style="color: #bdc3c7; margin-bottom:15px;">스마트 에너지 모니터링 시스템 전문 기업</p>
                <address style="font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6;">
                    부산광역시 범내골 kh 학원 <br>
                    대표전화: 051-123-4567 | 이메일: info@ess-ms.com
                </address>
                <p class="copyright" style="margin-top:15px; font-size:0.85rem; color:#95a5a6;">&copy; 2026 ESS-Monitoring System. All Rights Reserved.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-links">
                <h4 style="margin-bottom:15px;">Quick Links</h4>
                <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; line-height:2;">
                    <li><a href="1.main.html" style="color:#bdc3c7; text-decoration:none;">홈</a></li>
                    <li><a href="3.serviceInfo.html" style="color:#bdc3c7; text-decoration:none;">서비스 소개</a></li>
                    <li><a href="2.contact.html" style="color:#bdc3c7; text-decoration:none;">문의게시판</a></li>
                    <li><a href="7.newsupdate.html" style="color:#bdc3c7; text-decoration:none;">최신 정보</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-sns">
                <h4 style="margin-bottom:15px;">Follow Us</h4>
                <div class="sns-icons" style="display:flex; gap:15px; color:#bdc3c7;">
                    <span>Blog</span>
                    <span>LinkedIn</span>
                    <span>Youtube</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="js/7.newsupdate.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
